<p>It is super exciting for me because it definitely gives <a href="https://cspray.ca">cspray.ca</a> a new level of professionalism. Plus it looks super cool and official. Now that Iâ€™ve done it, I want to document the tl;dr of the process for myself and share with you along the way. I wish I would have done this sooner because it is really <strong>EASY</strong> to do.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Iâ€™ve had email catchers before but Iâ€™ve never had the opportunity to send emails from my own domain. Plus, Iâ€™ve been looking at trying out new tools for my email anyway. Iâ€™ve been with googleâ€™s email service since its inception. All of the things aligned.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>So here is the tl;dr of the requirements if you want to follow along.</p>

